<HEAD>Government Building Damaged in Blast</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PRAGUE, Czechoslovakia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An explosion caused substantial
damage in a local government building in the town of Usti nad Labem
early Wednesday in what the state news agency CTK described as a
