alone, the official MTI news agency said. The illegal activites
included theft, burglary and financial manipulation, the report
said, quoting figures from a recent study by the Supreme Court.
   Last summer, 25 people were tried in connection with an
international car smuggling ring which sold expensive Western cars
at high prices, the state-run media reported.
